cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (MM) techniques for RGB-T object tracking. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.MM are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel graph-based approach that involves optimization and learning, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of RGB-T object tracking in robotics (cs.RO), which is another likely sub-category.
